        "title": "Industry Collaborator",
        "content": "With a versatile, genre-spanning expertise, Lundun has engineered and composed alongside South Africa's music elite. Credits include: K.O, Kabza De Small, Kwesta, Jesse Clegg, Manana, Samthing Soweto, Msaki, Berita, Ndlovu Youth Choir, Sun El Musician, Thando Zide, and Simphiwe Dana."
